  "prompt": "What are some of the best poems in Hindi for mothers?",
  "response": "Here are some beautiful Hindi poems about mothers:\n\n1. \"\u092e\u093e\u0901\" by Harivansh Rai Bachchan\n- A deeply emotional poem praising a mother's unconditional love\n\n2. \"\u0924\u0941\u092e\u094d\u0939\u093e\u0930\u0940 \u092f\u093e\u0926\" by Dinesh Kumar\n- A poignant poem remembering a mother's sacrifices\n\n3. \"\u092e\u093e\u0901 \u0915\u093e \u092a\u094d\u092f\u093e\u0930\" by Ramdhari Singh Dinkar\n- Celebrates a mother's pure and selfless love\n\n4. \"\u092e\u093e\u0901\" by Mahadevi Verma\n- A powerful tribute to motherhood and maternal affection\n\n5. \"\u092e\u093e\u0924\u0943 \u0938\u094d\u0928\u0947\u0939\" by Sumitranandan Pant\n- Describes the depth of a mother's love and care\n\n6. \"\u092e\u093e\u0901 \u0915\u0947 \u091a\u0930\u0923\" by Gopal Singh Nepali\n- Expresses reverence and gratitude towards mothers\n\n7. \"\u092e\u093e\u0901 \u0915\u0940 \u092e\u092e\u0924\u093e\" by Shivmangal Singh Suman\n- Highlights a mother's nurturing nature\n\nThese poems beautifully capture the essence of maternal love, sacrifice, and the profound relationship between a mother and her child in the Hindi language.\n\nWould you like me to share the full text of any of these poems?",
